[24.927394, "o", "\r\n"]
[24.927776, "o", "  Every claim in the brief is bound to a STIX object ID. The verifier\r\n  walks the markdown, extracts every [type--uuid] reference, and\r\n  rejects any citation that doesn't resolve to a real bundle object.\r\n  That's the discipline a SOC needs before it can rely on LLM-\r\n  generated intel briefs.\r\n"]
